{"tid":1217544,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家唔好忘記已經被捕 或者將會被捕既朋友","createTime":"2019-06-13T13:19:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T03:18:14.000Z","uid":219681,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9863c7b404227161310e6dd08825c123102ed238","tid":1217544,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:19:17.000Z","msg":"【6.12 佔領】盧偉聰：「暴動」已拘 11 人 發射數枚橡膠彈 150 催淚彈 僅「低殺傷力武器」<br />\n2019/6/13 &mdash; 17:35<br />\n<br />\n昨日大批反送中示威者佔領金鐘一帶，最終爆發警民衝突並造成 80人受傷。警務處處長盧偉聰今日下午見記者，證實至今已經拘捕了<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">11人</span></span></strong>，涉及公眾地方內擾亂秩序、非法集會、襲警，及與暴動有關罪行。他又形容，昨日警方使用的都是「低殺傷力武器」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好俾眼前既平靜麻醉左</span></strong></strong></span><br />\n警察呢一兩日一定係繼續拘捕學生，目的就係為左打亂大家既部署同打擊大家既士氣<br />\n希望大家多多留意同關心被捕人士，更甚係可以提供任何形式既協助<br />\n希望媒體同議員可以多多跟進同保護被捕既同學<br />\n<br />\n我地只係表達訴求 <strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">拒絕無理政治檢控</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6b9ec69fef4343822affad1216484eb7b093d631","tid":1217544,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:19:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c5f243a1bb705295093b89bb22896ea6ac76d7","tid":1217544,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:27:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16874cd1207114e63397bdaf8a6bb03e311921d2","tid":1217544,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:32:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7233d10098fe390f0734dc4c9237b8c5cc20515","tid":1217544,"uid":35309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:58:27.000Z","msg":"佢有冇定義 係邊到 幾時  做咩<br />\n先會犯左暴動罪？"},{"pid":"4d8d2543111f8f4caa3